## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="59251-102">默认情况下<xref:System.Object> , 类型参数`VARIANT`作为类型进行封送处理, 其中对象类型`VARIANT`确定`VARTYPE`的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59251-102">By default, <xref:System.Object> type arguments are marshaled as a `VARIANT` type, where the object type determines the `VARTYPE` value of the `VARIANT`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="59251-103"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper>类型必须`VARIANT`作为类型进行<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper>封送处理, 否则类型将作为整数封送。 `VT_ERROR` <xref:System.Object></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59251-103">The <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> type must to be passed as an <xref:System.Object> type to be marshaled as a `VARIANT` of type `VT_ERROR`, otherwise the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> type is marshaled as an integer.</span></span>  
  
