 <span data-ttu-id="59251-127">请注意<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> , 在将对象从 COM `VT_ERROR`传递回后, 不会将其作为类型进行封送处理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59251-127">Note that <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> objects are not marshaled as type `VT_ERROR` after they are passed back from COM.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="59251-128">单个值作为类型`VT_I4`从 com 封送回, 而数组作为类型`VT_UI4`从 com 封送回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59251-128">A single value is marshaled back from COM as type `VT_I4`, while arrays are marshaled back from COM as type `VT_UI4`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="59251-129">有关的详细信息`VT_ERROR`, 请参阅 MSDN library `VARENUM::VT_ERROR`中的现有文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59251-129">For more information on `VT_ERROR`, please see the existing documentation for `VARENUM::VT_ERROR` in the MSDN library.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="59251-130">下面的代码示例首先演示如何将<xref:System.Int32>独立的对象<xref:System.Int32>作为对象从 COM 封送回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59251-130">The following code example first demonstrates a lone <xref:System.Int32> object marshaled back from COM as an <xref:System.Int32> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="59251-131">然后, 它演示<xref:System.Int32>从 COM 以数组的<xref:System.UInt32>形式封送回的数组。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="59251-131">It then demonstrates an <xref:System.Int32> array marshaled back from COM as a <xref:System.UInt32> array.</span></span>  
  
```  
// Scenario 1:  
// Pass a single value.  
Int32 x = 3;  
Object o = new ErrorWrapper(x);  
// Pass 'o' to COM.  
// On the return trip, 'o' has been unwrapped and is still an Int32 object.  
Int32 y = (Int32)o;  
Scenario 2:  
// Pass an array of values.  
Int32[] arr = new Int32[3];  
Object o = new ErrorWrapper(arr);  
// Pass 'o' to COM.  
// On the return trip, 'o' has been unwrapped and is now a UInt32[] array.  
UInt32[ ] arr2 = (UInt32[])o;  
```
